# method		the sample method used. 'sorted to species' means that an attempt was made to sort the biomass to species and any remaining biomass was classified as unsorted. 'not_ sorted' indicates that no attempt was made to sort the biomass to species and all of the biomass was classified as unsorted.
# biomass_g_m2	gramsPerSquareMeter	the dry weight of the biomass in grams/meter squared
# area_sampled	squareMeter	the area that was harvested for the sample in square meters
